
<p>I missed this story back in 2024, but it’s the same infuriating impulse toward infantilization <a href="https://daringfireball.net/linked/2025/10/11/bond-poster-guns">as with the Bond posters</a> this month. Amazon <a href="https://daringfireball.net/misc/2025/10/full-metal-jacket-poster-prime.jpeg">restored the correct poster art</a> for <em>Full Metal Jacket</em>, but they didn’t learn the lesson: <a href="https://x.com/MatthewModine/status/1802862920378052877">don’t fuck with art</a>.</p>

